{"tid":885821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：可派15,000名美軍到美墨邊境，即阿富汗戰爭的美軍規模","createTime":"2018-11-01T15:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T23:53:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2e38db01e532d9124062f038e8b3a2737bf5cc99","tid":885821,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1426179-20181101.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1426179-20181101.htm&d=pDHJKDQiVt9ZPbW1ih0ODsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=964522da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1426179-20181101.htm&h=9ae5edd6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1426179-20181101.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普警告，可以派遣多達15000名美軍到接壤墨西哥的邊境，阻截他形容為「危險」的難民。<br />\n<br />\n五角大樓早前表示，將派出最多7000人名軍人到邊境，特朗普提出的人數，較國防部原定的計劃多一倍，相當於阿富汗戰爭的美軍規模，被質疑是為了中期選舉造勢"},{"pid":"bb0595c8700b545e3f994e2e0739a66a8b7723a2","tid":885821,"uid":130105,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"港台睇左膠文章來翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc9c9f49c0485a397e0d0a4b37e03c3682f5bbf","tid":885821,"uid":196750,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:37:45.000Z","msg":"「難民」？！班公然偷渡客邊忽「難」先？中南美邊個國家打緊仗啊？<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母港台，亂譯左膠文，低質冇極限。"},{"pid":"a9cc1754a4de3b3131a2b3a2ff928e4008a12a0e","tid":885821,"uid":121146,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:39:25.000Z","msg":"被質疑是為了中期選舉造勢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老味奧巴馬執政果陣都有權咁做架喎  <br />\n又唔撚見條黑鬼對現承諾守護國土？"},{"pid":"6b8a2451ff8ca32e2829a53bf822f6c629105390","tid":885821,"uid":165377,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:42:40.000Z","msg":"從未見過如此臭串 明目張膽搭車去美國既難民"},{"pid":"faf3f2df3f23f5a82